      <title>FTSE Russell允许欧元，美元股票加入英国指数</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/ftse-russell-allows-euro-dollar-stocks-to-join-uk-indexes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[索引提供商FTSE Russell将允许以欧元和美元交易的股票加入英国主要的基准，此举可能有助于吸引伦敦上市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/ftse-russell-allows-euro-dollar-stocks-to-join-uk-indexes</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 18:44:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
